INSERT INTO transfer_targets VALUES(10,'2026-summer','Modou Kéba Cissé','시세',1944705,'LASK → Aston Villa','CB','RCB','CONFIRMED','00200001420237413X9814X84',60.89999999999999858,31.19999999999999929,6,6.769999999999999574,'cb_defender','Balanced','cb_bpd','Aggressive',0.8900000000000000133,'CONFIRMED incoming: pre-contract signed summer 2025, joins for 2026/27 after a season at LASK. Measured: right-of-centre CB (60.9,31.2), Ball-Playing Defender/Aggressive fit 0.89 — same fit family as Konsa (0.88). Natural RCB cover/heir; Austrian Bundesliga level caveat. [2026-07-15 재확인] RotoWire: 공식 합류 확인(사전계약, LASK에서 2026년 여름 발효). [2026-07-15 3축+스탯 — 유지] 6경기: kp 0·xA .01·듀얼 3.8·태클 1.5·패스 84% — 진전 산출 없는 수비형, cb_defender/Balanced 처방 유지(움직임은 bpd/Aggressive .89로 콘사형 스텝아웃 — 기능축 우선). LASK 리그 수준 캐비앗.','https://readastonvilla.com/2026/05/14/modou-keba-cisse-the-future-aston-villa-player-who-is-shining-in-austria/ ; SofaScore API player 1944705 (2026-07-02)','CONFIRMED signing; measured from LASK (league-strength caveat). / 2026-07-15: 공식 완료 확인 — CONFIRMED 유지.','시세');
INSERT INTO transfer_targets VALUES(11,'2026-summer','Zion Suzuki','스즈키',905351,'Parma','GK','GK','MEDIUM-HIGH','0000000000000000010001X20',50.29999999999999716,7.299999999999999823,6,7.129999999999999894,'gk_sweeper','Balanced','gk_goalkeeper','Defend',0.974999999999999978,'UPGRADED from USER WATCHLIST (2026-07-02 evening watch): ROMANO (tier-1) — Villa scouting Suzuki for months; he is on a 3-GK shortlist (with Trafford of Man City; 3rd unnamed, possibly Trubin) for the Martínez succession, as Martínez nears Juventus. Parma ask ~€30m (£26m); Leeds "battle" reported; Bayern/Inter/Napoli/ManU watching. Measured: goal-line GK (50.3,7.3), fit gk_goalkeeper/Defend 0.97; best sampled GK avg rating (7.13 at Parma). Sweeper/build-up retraining question stands, as with Trubin. [2026-07-15 재확인] 리세가 1순위이며 수즈키는 대안, 아직 구단간 컨택 전 에이전트 대상 탐색 단계. [2026-07-15 스탯 — 유지] 6경기: 선방 3.8/경기·패스 59%(마르티네스 55%와 유사 — 빌드업 결격 아님). 처방 유지.','https://www.teamtalk.com/aston-villa/villa-scouting-parma-keeper-zion-suzuki-three-man-shortlist-replace-emiliano-martinez ; https://sports.yahoo.com/articles/aston-villa-want-parma-goalkeeper-185000163.html ; SofaScore API player 905351 (2026-07-02)','MEDIUM-HIGH — [2026-07-14 재확인] 마르티네스 기사에서 "빌라 1순위 대체는 리세르, 스즈키는 대안"으로 우선순위 하락 확인. 뉴캐슬이 협상 개시(negotiations)로 경쟁 심화. tier-1(Romano) 관심 보도는 유지. 등급 유지. / 2026-07-15 재확인: 리세르가 1옵션, 수즈키는 대안으로 순위 하락 지속.','스즈키');
